{"id":"15209755298","name":"Riverbed scramble towards \u201cWhite Rock\u201d","type":"Hike","date":"2025-07-23T12:32:32","description":"Polybius talks about a prominent white rock that provided some shelter for his troops while they were being harassed by locals. Bramans (en route to the Col de Clapier) has an extremely prominent white rock face. Whether this is what Polybius was talking about we cannot say. Didn\u2019t get near enough to really assess how his troops could have benefitted from it, since I\u2019m not quite as tough as Hannibal \u2014I didn\u2019t want to get wet feet.\n\n(Trail actually shows the return journey)","distance_mi":0.75,"moving_time_s":1206,"elevation_m":3.2,"avg_hr":88,"max_hr":102,"avg_cadence":51,"calories":140,"with_pet":null,"with_kid":null,"has_track":true,"track":{"type":"LineString","coordinates":[[6.791058,45.223854,1150.6],[6.790812,45.223874,1217.2],[6.790755,45.22387,1217.4],[6.790715,45.22384,1217.4],[6.790631,45.22388,1217.8],[6.790584,45.223932,1218.4],[6.79055,45.223943,1218.6],[6.790526,45.223964,1219.0],[6.790469,45.223984,1219.6],[6.790444,45.223993,1220.2],[6.790423,45.223992,1220.2],[6.79041,45.224012,1221.6],[6.790367,45.224035,1225.6],[6.79036,45.224035,1227.0],[6.790317,45.224021,1229.2],[6.790223,45.22403,1231.6],[6.790178,45.224011,1232.6],[6.790128,45.223981,1233.2],[6.790099,45.223999,1233.2],[6.790009,45.22401,1236.8],[6.78991,45.224044,1238.6],[6.789866,45.224069,1241.2],[6.789783,45.224095,1244.8],[6.789741,45.224107,1246.4],[6.789709,45.224111,1247.8],[6.789658,45.224106,1248.4],[6.789578,45.224105,1249.2],[6.789546,45.224095,1249.4],[6.789518,45.224094,1249.4],[6.789466,45.224091,1249.6],[6.789421,45.224091,1250.0],[6.789397,45.224075,1251.4],[6.789316,45.22403,1254.6],[6.789252,45.224003,1254.8],[6.789187,45.223969,1255.4],[6.789105,45.22396,1256.2],[6.789028,45.223955,1257.2],[6.789001,45.223933,1258.8],[6.788978,45.223915,1260.8],[6.788947,45.223922,1262.2],[6.788947,45.223921,1262.4],[6.788907,45.22389